{"tid":1468431,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"想講好撚耐","createTime":"2019-08-13T18:39:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T19:48:51.000Z","uid":229790,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fabbec22b78a01d53e1a7b6c2bf3b38e12adcde8","tid":1468431,"uid":229790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:39:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以氣用事嘅你，唔撚該睇清楚</span></span><br />\n首先 核彈都唔撚割 但希望你存有理性<br />\n727 元朗<br />\n前線嘅唔係前線 係細路 退防線都唔齊 我一個人行到最前 控兩條線 慢慢推佢地 <br />\n中段 啲狗12 12咁推 我地又12 12咁推<br />\n當狗同我地差唔多相隔兩三個身位 有人係後面掉磚<br />\n結果啲狗即衝 我望住個前線跑唔切 比狗拉入人堆 即打 <br />\n<br />\n813 機場<br />\n打完人 唔比人走 救護黎咗 都走唔到<br />\n最後要叫狗黎幫拖 衝曬出去打警車 呢個冇問題<br />\n但當機場保安清 你地屌都算 記者清 你地屌<br />\n記者幫我地頂幾撚多？你知唔撚知？<br />\n你係側邊打 打撚完 有位走 前線 幫你頂 <br />\n係呀 你發洩完 打完 最後邊個比人拉？<br />\n前線呀 屌你老尾！<br />\n仲要塞撚住個門 想救人都出唔到去<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">做野唔該睇時機！</span><br />\n<br />\n仲有樣 813塞機場離境大堂<br />\n有個老人家 話做完手術 <br />\n佢係唔係作都好 唔該比番啲理性同人性<br />\n抗爭、行動唔係冇腦咁去進行<br />\n無領袖狀態下 一定存在好多嘅彈性<br />\n但拉共識嘅時候 唔好撚淨係屌付出幾多<br />\n真係比個平台大家講下<br />\n<br />\n最後奉上天琦一句：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我懇請你們不要被仇恨支配自己，在危難中，仍要時刻保持警覺與思考。</span></span>"},{"pid":"d5681194e02c4e97a3554d862e43fecddbe99d40","tid":1468431,"uid":229790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:40:52.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"abdd1ec47f121b807aa9999ec384ee6e12cf7c30","tid":1468431,"uid":229790,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:41:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"79f25243aa1122dfd743126f2314a8aa4dcbe60f","tid":1468431,"uid":117550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:43:38.000Z","msg":"(突發)航空公司   民航處  機管局講大話<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468306\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468306</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fbda5fb25af7dcd2a3ef9c59c69d65d3d58c4c22","tid":1468431,"uid":98842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5681194e02c4e97a3554d862e43fecddbe99d40","tid":1468431,"uid":229790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:40:52.000Z","msg":"自推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:44:12.000Z","msg":"【訓撚醒未呀】港共政府 無辦法係機場清場 但 可以 連登分化粉碎呢個活動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467822\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467822</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">試下用 我不會放棄機場 回覆</span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/12DZA4k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F12DZA4k.png&h=5f8f09e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1cb69ee00224b14a72d59b4ac5abb12008655e46","tid":1468431,"uid":277519,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:45:38.000Z","msg":"推。視其他人死活不顧。不值"},{"pid":"b3b1d96eb3090c2a809952929349022eb4da3d4e","tid":1468431,"uid":229790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:26:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d6a17a35775c90e481437a8fd330673469757ff6","tid":1468431,"uid":229790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:27:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"70f856e6c9ee0eda5371eb829c88ac3f361bb8b2","tid":1468431,"uid":229790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:28:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c7be7bb29b5a7fa00fbb2c93b087f6b419cf450e","tid":1468431,"uid":140460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:37:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9763131fa4b20aa29f67705b705a7ae4593dc727","tid":1468431,"uid":229790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:44:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"814e46dd5e6adcfd7190ac5ed9a53f9dc4b68235","tid":1468431,"uid":274180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:48:51.000Z","msg":"不分化不割席 只檢討與改進 我要贏啊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468585\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468585</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}